race.comment: Small field but good race. Looking down in the weights. SWEET PROPOSAL (5) has been flying lately with wins in her last two in easier grade. Has led throughout and not been caught, and with the big weight drop will take beating again. SILVER WARRIOR (6) is another down in the weights and the other leader in the race. Super consistent record lately but all his best form is on the all-weather. Drops massively in the weights on the last couple though with the claim and in this small field will give a sight. CHAYSE 'N' ARTIE (3) lifted strongly to score in easier grade at Ipswich last time over a similar trip. Nice weight drop for this and will stalk the leading pair. INVER PARK (1) was beaten in a photo here two back then safely held at Eagle Farm last time. Will find this easier and despite the big weight will be winding up late. WARP SPEED (2) is the interesting runner resuming from a good break. Has the ability and also an in-form claimer. Worth keeping safe.
